snippet.title: ZERO PROTOCOL Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Add to wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2840250/ZERO_PROTOCOL/

In this sci-fi survival horror game, you have to uncover the secrets of the IAS Antarctic research complex, decide the fate of humanity and try to survive.
